snippet.title: Rockstar gameplay (PC Game, 1989)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Rockstar, Dos PC game produced by Wizard Games in 1989 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/rockstar/629/
Rockstar is an interesting game, a text adventure. You're a rock star role and must earn as much popularity. You're writing songs, composing, do you realize videos and campaigns in the world.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
